| 4 | Goal ID shows "none" | `grpc_client.py:329`, `__main__.py:81` | Apply `_pb_to_dict()` to create_goal return; use dict `.get()` for safe access |
| 5 | 20-30s cycle time | `loop.py:302-335, 421-430` | Skip Vision eye when DOM Reader is sufficient; rate-limit Vision to every 3rd cycle; skip Verifier on intermediate steps |
| 6 | Excess Chrome launches | `session.rs:54-84` | Reuse idle sessions by goal_id before launching new Chrome |
